    "gp_section_625369882908688947": {
      "type": "gp-section-625369882908688947",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "de385a5a42ab099c40c2a7c8919afcde7f760c9e3a12971f99e2bf73132c60ac_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_0": "<p>Why You'll Love It  </p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_1": "<p>Size &amp; Fit</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_2": "<p>Fabrics &amp; Care</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_3": "<p>45 Day Perfect Fit Money Guarantee</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_4": "<p>Anti-Hole Guarantee</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_5": "<p>Free Returns &amp; Exchanges</p>",
        "ggMOFdfwuZp_text": "<p>BoxHero Bamboo Boxer Shorts are crafted from ultra-stretchy bamboo fabric, making them 83% more durable than conventional boxers. Designed for ultimate breathability, they neutralize odors and wick away moisture, keeping you fresh, comfortable, and confident all day long – no matter where life takes you</p>",
        "gg1n7ZOO0-b_text": "<p>Details:</p>",
        "ggONRFY2ZJc_text": "<ul>\n<li>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>No-Roll Waistband</strong></span> that won't pinch or bunch</li>\n<li>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>Hypoallergenic</strong></span> skin-safe fabric </li>\n<li>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>Anti-odor</strong></span> BambooFiber™ Technology</li>\n<li>HeroMesh™ <span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>360° Cooling Zones</strong></span>\n</li>\n<li>Supportive <span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>Contour Pouch </strong></span>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>Pre-Shrunk</strong></span> to avoid laundry shrinking</li>\n</ul>",
        "ggY2hH_XtMS_text": "<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Boxhero Bamboo Boxer Shorts</strong> <span style=\"color:#313131;\">have a snug, supportive fit, designed to stay in place throughout the day.</span>\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Take your normal size</strong> <span style=\"color:#313131;\">in boxer briefs.</span>\n</li>\n</ul>",
        "ggylOGhWg62_text": "<p>Body Measurements</p>",
        "gghJgaCYjNP_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>Waist</strong></span></p><p>in</p>",
        "ggYsr3DLl0H_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>Waist</strong></span></p><p>cm</p>",
        "ggrzqZGt_jj_text": "<p>S</p>",
        "gg6FyGa3apR_text": "<p>30-31</p>",
        "ggo8ElaZcig_text": "<p>76-78</p>",
        "ggeR4bUufTV_text": "<p>M</p>",
        "gg3xLhRxEhT_text": "<p>32-33</p>",
        "gg9h1exo3hm_text": "<p>81-84</p>",
        "ggvTGprVUnW_text": "<p>L</p>",
        "ggSG-PVMSvO_text": "<p>34-37</p>",
        "ggYGs69FCaJ_text": "<p>85-93</p>",
        "ggeFgXsgSFe_text": "<p>XL</p>",
        "ggTkLsyPB4F_text": "<p>38-43</p>",
        "ggaFfzg8CK6_text": "<p>94-105</p>",
        "ggAXiE1gSor_text": "<p>2XL</p>",
        "ggmzpfLufmi_text": "<p>43+</p>",
        "ggd3JoQWjf4_text": "<p>105+</p>",
        "ggkEmYBp-0H_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>PRO TIP:</strong></span> If you’re in between sizes or prefer a looser fit, consider sizing up</p>",
        "ggqhBhWDBtQ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-3668000f-9259-4130-90bc-90b334c37ec7.png",
        "gg_SGag8dAL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-8432f01a-70e3-413e-b123-425198d89541.svg",
        "ggS4J8xidtx_text": "<p>SOFTNESS</p>",
        "ggwn-GKtqmn_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-b179c129-a2aa-441e-85d1-6b14dfe85d5b.svg",
        "ggB0brh0_Fp_text": "<p>STRETCH</p>",
        "gg4e1Pb0NWx_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-b179c129-a2aa-441e-85d1-6b14dfe85d5b.svg",
        "ggwy6VviEya_text": "<p>BREATHABILITY</p>",
        "ggIWSuErOmh_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-99e68524-3c41-4592-84e6-89ad5a5ced24.svg",
        "ggTtlCbl8iP_text": "<p>WEIGHT</p>",
        "gg5omjG4FTY_text": "<p>Our innovative Bamboo Powered BoxHero™ Fabrics boasts a buttery soft feel with ultimate stretch, support and breathability, making it one of our most-loved and sold out boxers of all times.</p>",
        "ggke2kdjjPM_text": "<p>Did you know ?</p>",
        "ggsTCZ-Um--_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>Bamboo</strong></span> is one of the <span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>strongest and most durable</strong></span> natural fibers, which is why we chose it for our Boxhero Boxer Shorts.</p>",
        "ggYcGmaU_82_text": "<p>About our guarantee</p>",
        "ggY4PV1YwiP_text": "<p>We’re confident in our quality, so we offer a <span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>45-Day Guarantee</strong></span>. Try them, and if they don’t fit or feel right, just email us for a new pair or a full refund—no questions asked.</p>",
        "ggZPjVhekCZ_text": "<p><strong>Customer Email:</strong> info@boxhero.co</p>",
        "ggS3SEZqTgt_text": "<p><strong>Got a hole in your boxer?</strong> No problem! If your boxer develops a tear <span style=\"background-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);color:#00237E;\"><strong>within 6 months,</strong></span> send it back to us and we’ll replace it for free. BoxHero is built to last, and we stand by our commitment to quality.</p>",
        "gg3NKTpOzbt_text": "<p>We believe in hassle-free shopping. That’s why Boxhero Bamboo Boxer Shorts come with <span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>free returns and exchanges.</strong></span> </p><p> </p><p>If they don’t fit just right or you’re not completely satisfied, simply return or exchange them at no cost to you. Enjoy comfort without any risk.</p>",
        "gg9djR-c3ZU_childItem_0": "<p>reviews</p>",
        "ggHxm-K0LAX_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggWSJUxnYcX_text": "<p>The most comfortable… </p>",
        "gg5g09zhY8N_text": "<p>Absolutely the most comfortable underwear I’ve ever bought. They fit perfectly, stay in place, and feel like a second skin.</p>",
        "gg-tUtWxKhh_text": "<p>Liam H.</p>",
        "ggs_s6lEDOC_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggSV8qjUIF1_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggaAE89r1UW_text": "<p>I’ve tried many brands but..</p>",
        "ggcrnmF_lIE_text": "<p>I’ve tried many brands, but these boxers are on a whole different level. They’re incredibly soft, supportive, and durable.</p>",
        "ggLi9e3uAk2_text": "<p>Olivier J.</p>",
        "ggAGzVndjra_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggeny5F_KBU_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "gg1o0gkxDYu_text": "<p>As an avid runner </p>",
        "ggiBPVdR7g-_text": "<p>As a runner, finding the right underwear is crucial. These offer excellent support and breathability. They keep me dry and comfortable</p>",
        "ggJai-mIzBo_text": "<p>Avery N.</p>",
        "gg5qyYTYLNz_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggRSQR38XsP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "gghO-CfoMnU_text": "<p>No odor or sweat, this bamboo really works!</p>",
        "ggdBeG9LSOZ_text": "<p>My partner says they’re the most comfortable he’s ever worn. After multiple washes, they keep their shape and softness.</p>",
        "ggFJhv6XtFa_text": "<p>Camelia J.</p>",
        "ggNfcoKkxKB_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "gg6_EEbztta_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggMh8UP1KeW_text": "<p>Satisfied beyond belief!!!! </p>",
        "ggpTskvks_G_text": "<p>Two weeks of walking around Europe, constantly adjusting and sweating. After switching to Boxhero, the comfort blew me away. 100% satisfied!</p>",
        "ggAEVbUSJBl_text": "<p>Marc C.</p>",
        "gg-oS0OaV7f_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "gg_q4SQCEgL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggMXtYiLE4i_text": "<p>UNREAL comfort</p>",
        "ggZ5ZjGQGbG_text": "<p>These boxers are like a hug—soft, supportive, and luxurious. They stay in place all day, even after multiple washes. </p>",
        "ggiCWw-UEx6_text": "<p>Jason K.</p>",
        "ggD_fPnY0sn_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "gg8vkzyRom3_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-f2ab390a-662e-4a0e-bf4c-237bc7b9d578.svg",
        "ggLbdEuXnjp_text": "<p>Rated <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong>4.6</strong></span>/ 5 based on <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong><u>3800+ Customers.</u></strong></span></p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_625369883093238323": {
      "type": "gp-section-625369883093238323",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "6d68493f3dbf8c4f82d57a73c659e33277bd669988c1fe7b1aa26a9c5ea55d46_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggbH-IVQ7BE_text": "<p>4.8/5 based on 3438 reviews</p>",
        "gga1VaOr4fd_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/Template_Avis_Cadre_Photo_1.png",
        "ggmAceQtFS9_text": "50,481+",
        "gglsj97MMsI_text": "Happy Customers",
        "ggPmGwwLfeb_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/Image_2316x3088_f25ee40f-e34d-4bf0-bb00-78ef5f4ea2a3.webp",
        "ggCE7fHYrbV_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\">Husband Approves, and so do i ;) </span>",
        "ggyX7DdMLJ__text": "<p>My husband was fed up with uncomfortable underwear that didn’t last. After switching to BoxHero, he’s thrilled with how soft and comfortable they are—even after multiple washes. And the best part? No more sagging or fading! And honestly, I love how good he looks in them.</p>",
        "ggT835CQDCm_text": "<p>Carole j.</p>",
        "ggL1j6OyWH8_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggHo-yWyVXU_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://boxhero.co/cdn/shop/files/gempages_491320059759690869-7540b399-dfa0-4ce4-b990-3587241f8916.jpg?v=7705973051629767699",
        "gg7uT70rLT8_text": "<span style=\"color:#09090A;\">no odor or sweat, this really works!</span>",
        "ggpcGRoEQhT_text": "<p>After a full day of work, there's no sweat or odor. I feel fresh from morning till night—best pair I've ever owned, and I wish I had bought these earlier in my life. I will definitely be ordering 5 more pairs in the next few months.</p>",
        "gguY7QvohhM_text": "<p>ron d.</p>",
        "gg2EiQA_kVZ_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggku5Q9ZIvW_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/17_85d6016f-94c1-4ff7-a959-2a48bfc513ff.jpg",
        "ggbNlt912uz_text": "<span style=\"color:#09090A;\">The size is good, material is good, waist band is good</span>",
        "ggaIIux6kpV_text": "<p>I have tried so many different underwear, just to throw them away. These I like. The size is good, material is good, waist band is good, pouch is good, and they are holding up well. They have not faded, the waist band has not lost any strength, and they seem to work perfect. I am giving them a five stars because they fit and feel good wearing, and they look good too.</p>",
        "gghbdWf1S0I_text": "<p>Tommy G.</p>",
        "ggXodWLXYj9_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggvOiRjsRSc_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://boxhero.co/cdn/shop/files/gempages_491320059759690869-99c7d589-1f15-4fb4-908a-747d39743ceb.jpg?v=11217554910590163594",
        "ggtXh0XHscb_text": "ultra soft, i need 20 more pairs!",
        "ggWYmWxn-eN_text": "<p>The fabric of BoxHero is so soft, I no longer deal with that irritating rubbing I used to get from other brands that cost me 2x more. Plus, they stay fresh all day—10/10 for comfort and durability!</p>",
        "ggB0JxMJuZo_text": "<p>Samuel p.</p>",
        "ggjmKYCRCBG_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggWe6XmJzW1_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-ab728eca-73f8-494e-a092-8eb595a9c948.jpg",
        "ggWe6XmJzW1_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/Capture_d_ecran_2025-03-31_a_09.39.51.png",
        "gga14oHm6kL_text": "<span style=\"color:#09090A;\">wife approves, and i love them </span>",
        "ggoFT06VXY4_text": "<p>The breathability of these shorts is simply exceptional. No matter what I’m doing, I always feel comfortable and fresh. Bamboo really does make all the difference—honestly, these are life-changing. Plus, my wife approves, and I love them!</p>",
        "ggsa-JkQbqv_text": "<p>Alex N.</p>",
        "ggiUNvvbYkT_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggaplnOalc2_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-c787c8d9-660e-47cf-a44b-e4d573d9168a.jpg",
        "ggj55v5oBWj_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\">I’m a big guy, and these stay put!</span>",
        "ggWpEm7o-W0_text": "<p>'m a big guy, and these fit great. No riding up—they stay in place. They feel amazing, and there's no chafing, even on heavy workdays. This is my second set, and the first still looks and feels the same after six months. I'm replacing all my old boxers with BoxHero Bamboo boxers.</p>",
        "ggSo3tb0KO9_text": "<p>John M.</p>",
        "ggqtOcmPD1Q_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "gg1AzXVMlQj_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-eb915671-cc65-4d4c-a788-db3d8ae5237e.jpg",
        "ggtb5aRMmlI_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\">all day comfort and no moisture</span>",
        "ggcmHQakp1d_text": "<p>I've bought the Boxhero, which has a natural soft and comfortable feel and does an excellent job of wicking moisture. These are the most comfortable ones I have ever worn!</p>",
        "ggBEBA7Z0To_text": "<p>Walt f.</p>",
        "ggSRlEt7zg6_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggTzJSpgZ7w_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-8edc889b-e32f-4ced-8ab4-d36250a9de00.png",
        "ggW6i3PixrQ_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\">Finally boxer shorts That don't rip... and smell GOOD!</span>",
        "ggErwWMd-6O_text": "<p>Finally, boxer shorts that don't rip... and smell GOOD! Super comfortable. I've been a fan of CK for many years but these are superior. They fit perfectly and don't ride up throughout the day. So comfortable and great visually; love that feeling of 'being cradled'. Thoroughly recommended.</p>",
        "ggxQbXj5HuA_text": "<p>Jeff C.</p>",
        "ggNL_LQAxfd_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_625369882925466163": {
      "type": "gp-section-625369882925466163",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "9a5460415ec433dbbc15cf9ebd4d20b4ce04fd53edd4d5753a43a5dea93f4d5f_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggX2EniVm9q_text": "FAQ",
        "ggvyreBNINt_text": "<p>Still have questions ? Check here</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_0": "<p>What is bamboo fibre and why is it used for boxer shorts?</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_1": "<p>Why do dermatologists recommend bamboo fibre boxers? </p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_2": "<p>How does the breathability of bamboo fibre boxers differ from other materials? </p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_3": "<p>What does the “buy 2 + 3 free” offer mean? </p>",
