        "gggxLjRu8yN_text": "<p>The exceptional breathability of our bamboo fibre boxers allows air to circulate, reducing humidity and perspiration. You will always feel comfortable and fresh, whatever your activity.</p>",
        "ggrxGymrlkU_text": "<p>Our special offer allows you to buy 2 bamboo fibre boxer shorts and receive 3 free. This is a limited opportunity to renew your collection of high-quality underwear. Not to be missed!</p>",
        "ggkDSqjyiH9_text": "<p>Bamboo fibre boxer shorts are designed for added durability thanks to their high-quality material. They are more resistant to wear and last longer than regular boxers.</p>",
        "ggoQB6YO3wQ_text": "<p>Yes, in general, bamboo fibre boxers are suitable for sensitive skin due to their softness and ability to reduce skin irritation. However, if you have specific concerns, we recommend consulting a healthcare professional.</p>",
        "ggkYAJ7acNt_text": "<p>Yes, our bamboo fibre boxers are machine-washable. Please follow the care instructions included with your boxers for best washing practices.</p>",
        "ggQ0Wtpv_Ah_label": "<p>TRY IT RISK-FREE – TODAY AT 50% OFF!</p>",
